      <title>美国汽车制造商大厅将低成本汽车零件排除在关税之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-automakers-lobby-to-exclude-low-cost-car-parts-from-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，美国汽车制造商正在游说特朗普政府将某些车辆零件排除在关税之外，这是在本周开始生效之前在他们开始生效之前要影响征费的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-automakers-lobby-to-exclude-low-cost-car-parts-from-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 21:32:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社会保障网站崩溃，因为代理商将用户推向在线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/social-security-website-crashes-as-agency-pushes-users-online</link>
      <description><![CDATA[社会保障局表示，正在调查最近发生的事件的原因，这些事件阻止了受益人在门户网站暂时下降后无法访问其在线帐户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/social-security-website-crashes-as-agency-pushes-users-online</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 21:28:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
